<dl><dt><big>class <u>PropertyFile</u>;
</big></dt>
<dd>A class to facilitate reading of XML property files.
<br><br>
Currently supports string, int, string[] and int[] properties.
<br><br>

 Two styles of XML are supported:
<pre class="d_code">&lt;?xml <font color=blue>version</font>=<font color=red>"1.0"</font> ?&gt;
   &lt;Properties layout=<font color=red>"1"</font>&gt;
      &lt;constr type=<font color=red>"string"</font>&gt;Driver=SQL Server;DSN=MySQL1&lt;/constr&gt;
      &lt;logpath type=<font color=red>"string"</font>&gt;d:<font color=red>\</font>logs&lt;/logpath&gt;
      &lt;numlogs type=<font color=red>"int"</font>&gt;10&lt;/numlogs&gt;
      &lt;maxlogsize type=<font color=red>"int"</font>&gt;1000000&lt;/maxlogsize&gt;
      &lt;watchdirs type=<font color=red>"string[]"</font>&gt;
         &lt;item&gt;d:<font color=red>\</font>A&lt;/item&gt;
         &lt;item&gt;d:<font color=red>\</font>B&lt;/item&gt;
         &lt;item&gt;d:<font color=red>\</font>C&lt;/item&gt;
      &lt;/watchdirs&gt;
      &lt;thingie type=<font color=red>"int[]"</font>&gt;
         &lt;item&gt;1&lt;/item&gt;
         &lt;item&gt;2&lt;/item&gt;
         &lt;item&gt;3&lt;/item&gt;
      &lt;/thingie&gt;
   &lt;/Properties&gt;
</pre>
<br><br>
<b>and:</b><br>
<pre class="d_code">&lt;?xml <font color=blue>version</font>=<font color=red>"1.0"</font> ?&gt;
&lt;Properties layout=<font color=red>"2"</font>&gt;
   &lt;constr type=<font color=red>"string"</font> value=<font color=red>"Driver=SQL Server;DSN=MySQL1"</font> /&gt;
   &lt;logpath type=<font color=red>"string"</font> value=<font color=red>"d:\logs"</font> /&gt;
   &lt;numlogs type=<font color=red>"int"</font> value=<font color=red>"10"</font> /&gt;
   &lt;maxlogsize type=<font color=red>"int"</font> value=<font color=red>"1000000"</font> /&gt;
   &lt;watchdirs type=<font color=red>"string[]"</font>&gt;
      &lt;item value=<font color=red>"d:\A"</font> /&gt;
      &lt;item value=<font color=red>"d:\B"</font> /&gt;
      &lt;item value=<font color=red>"d:\C"</font> /&gt;
   &lt;/watchdirs&gt;
   &lt;thingie type=<font color=red>"int[]"</font>&gt;
      &lt;item value=<font color=red>"1"</font> /&gt;
      &lt;item value=<font color=red>"2"</font> /&gt;
      &lt;item value=<font color=red>"3"</font> /&gt;
   &lt;/thingie&gt;
&lt;/Properties&gt;
</pre>
 
<br><br>

